maintext:
AUSTIN, Texas (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Texas Lottery’s “Daily 4 Night” game were:
9-4-2-2, FIREBALL: 3
(nine, four, two, two; FIREBALL: three)
